These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, scientific, comedy, thriller
4 different games are played: chess, whist, canasta, backgammon
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, gardening, puzzles, writing
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, skateboard, ship, thrillercher
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, funk, r&b
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, coral, blue, green
 1. the person driving the thrillercher is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching comedy movies is the fan of classical##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is the person playing backgammon##1
 6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the person driving the ship is between the person who likes aquamarine and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
10. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person driving the ship and the person playing backgammon##2
11. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
12. the person driving the thrillercher is the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the fan of funk is between the fan of dubstep and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Movie-Genre      | thriller        | scientific       | comedy  | epic |
| Game          | backgammon     | canasta         | whist     | chess    |
| Hobby         | gardening  | fishing      | puzzles   | writing     |
| Transport           | skateboard | motorbike | ship   | thrillercher     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | funk         | classical | r&b         |
| Color         | green     | aquamarine     | coral  | blue       |

