.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, turquise, light-blue, chestnut
City: san-francisco, paris, berlin, venice
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, folk, gospel
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, game, montecristo, davidoff
House: art-deco, craftsman, ranch-style, townhouse
 1. the game-smoker is between the person traveling to berlin and the art-deco house##2
 2. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
 4. the game-smoker is between the person who likes blue and the ranch-style house##2
 5. the fan of disco is the person who likes turquise##1
 6. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
 7. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the ranch-style house is between the person watching action movies and the person traveling to venice##2
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the person traveling to venice##1
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
11. the fan of disco is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
13. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the craftsman house##1
14. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Color      | chestnut    | turquise       | light-blue   | blue |
| City         | san-francisco     | berlin   | venice    | paris  |
