 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is between the person who likes red and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
10. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
11. the person drinking tea is the person who likes azure##1
12. the palace house is the person who likes ebony##1
